title: *UNLOCKED* Patreon Ep #166: Revenge in Riddle City Part 1

description:
There's a lot more insanity where this came from! If you want to help support the show and listen to 100+ (almost 200!) more of these eps, you can subscribe at Patreon 

Ratman and Swallow, Riddle Cities’ favorite superhero/sidekick duo, face their greatest challenge yet when their nemesis Riddle-Her returns for revenge. This weeks guest is Olivia Nielsen as Horse Girl. This is a three part series and will feature six appearances from comedians as riddle cities most dastardly villains. Special thanks to Arne and Casey for all their hard work on this episode.
